# Chatvioso UI Component Map

## Purpose

This document defines the exact UI components that should exist in the Chatvioso frontend after the refactor.

It serves as:

- component inventory
- implementation checklist
- structure map for Cursor
- guide for reusable UI composition

The goal is to ensure the UI is rebuilt systematically instead of screen by screen with duplicated code.

---

# 1. Component Map Philosophy

The component map should follow these rules:

- shared first
- feature-specific where needed
- components should be small and composable
- avoid giant components
- avoid duplicate variants of the same UI pattern
- every major screen should be assembled from reusable blocks

