# 8. Message Bubble Variant Map

Message UI should not be built as one giant component.

## Subcomponents by responsibility

### Content rendering

- MessageBubbleText
- MessageBubbleAttachments
- MessageBubbleImage
- MessageBubbleFile

### Metadata rendering

- MessageTimestamp
- MessageBubbleStatus
- MessageSenderName for group chats if needed

### Layout wrappers

- MessageBubble
- MessageGroup
- DateSeparator

## Variants message UI must handle

- own text message
- other text message
- grouped own message
- grouped other message
- image attachment message
- file attachment message
- system message
- pending/sending message if supported
- failed message if supported

