# 17. File/Folder Build Checklist

Recommended folder pattern for major components:

```
FeatureName/
  ComponentName.tsx
  index.ts
  types.ts
  constants.ts
  utils.ts
```

Example:

```
features/messages/components/MessageBubble/
  MessageBubble.tsx
  index.ts
  types.ts
```

For smaller components, a single file is enough.

---

# 18. Component Dependency Rules

## Allowed pattern

- `features/*` can use `components/ui`
- `features/*` can use `components/shared`
- feature components can use their own feature-local components
- shared components can use ui primitives

## Avoid

- feature A deeply depending on feature B UI internals
- circular component dependency
- app layout importing low-level feature-specific message rendering without proper boundaries

